author: mrdon
msg: Adding warning messages when various parts of the Struts configuration
are overridden.  This allows one Struts config to override another, yet
informs the user in case it is by accident.
This is an empty revision for padding.

author: wrowe
msg: Fatal compiler quirk, you would think (DWORD)(n >> 32) == 0
if n is a DWORD.  But, alas, in release builds it doesn't.

author: mbo
msg: Support for single field identity in the JDO model. The ObjectId class defaults
to a subclass of SingleFieldIdentity if the pc class does not declare a ObjectId
class, but a single primary key field.
